which was discovered by an employee Sunday during maintenance at
Green Lane reservoir in north London.
   Scotland Yard spokesman Terry Norman said there was no apparent
connection between the find and recent arrests or terrorist activity.
   ``The explosives appear to have been abandoned, possibly by
someone throwing them into the reservoir from the road,'' he said.
