   Travel to attract recreational gardeners this season includes a
package tour to Britain and a flower festival in North Carolina.
   Wilton House in Wiltshire, the Lake District, Castle Howard in
Yorkshire, Anglesey Abbey in North Wales, Nottinghamshire, Leeds
Castle in Kent and the Chelsea Flower Show in London are on the
