much higher inflation and interest rates might go, and what effects
they might have on economic growth in the months ahead.
   Among actively traded blue chips, McDonald's dropped } to 49{;
General Electric slipped [ to 45[; International Business Machines
fell ] to 120}, and DuPont was down [ at 94~.
